HEADWORD: Wherever
<hw>Wher*ev"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>At or in whatever
place; wheresoever.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He can not but love virtue <qex>wherever</qex> it is.</q>
<rj><qau>Atterbury.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wherewith</ent>⟦br⟧
